This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition systems. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it involves processing audio signals. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SI (Signal Processing) as it involves processing signals from multiple channels. The use of Highway LSTM also suggests that it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of advanced neural network architectures.
